# turbo-adam

Turborepo monorepo: React 19 SPA + NestJS 11 API + Prisma 7 + PostgreSQL 17 + Redis 7.

## Why?

A hub for my projects and portfolio in a single repository. Turborepo orchestrates builds, caches tasks, and keeps frontend, backend, shared packages, and infrastructure in one place — no juggling multiple repos.

If you're looking for a structured way to grow your developer portfolio, this setup can be a good starting point.

## Tech stack

| Layer               | Technology                                        | Version     |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- | ----------- |
